{
  "stem": "58.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If they found you were on a train or on a bus that you went somewhere as a Jew, they took you there, and you never came out.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this was going on through the winter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When the summer came, the rumor was starting that we're going to go to Warsaw Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was already from 1939.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I'm thinking if I didn't skip anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Yeah, they formed a Judenrat in the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They usually picked people that are not any better than the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and if you were a friend of theirs, they tried-- they got you out of the working situation.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "If not, they picked the poor people or the people that didn't care for them, they made them work, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "On different-- you worked for the gendarmes, you worked for the SS, you worked-- in every place that they could spare people to go on the front.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they'd put people to work, instead of using soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Well, this was going on, like I said, to the, till-- in meantime, the Warsaw Ghetto was formed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they start putting people from all over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were told we're going to move to the Warsaw Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "This was beginning of 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they told us to prepare-- the Judenrat told us to prepare.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Put in everything in suitcases, you couldn't take any furniture.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You could only take what you could carry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they tricked us to put everything together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Then when we had to go to the ghetto, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they took us into this post office, where the SS was staying.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They took everything away, beat the hell out of us, and told us to go.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
